<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="雜科聲德" xml:id="gsz0894c23shiHaoZhi"><lb
n="0894c23" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0894c23"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>上都大安國寺<persName key="A008821">好直</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0894c24"/><persName key="A008821">釋好直</persName>，俗姓丁氏，會稽<placeName key="PL000000013376">諸暨</placeName>人也。幼不喜<lb
ed="T" n="0894c25"/>俗事，酒肉葷茹，天然不食。因投<placeName key="PL000000013360">杭塢山</placeName><persName key="A009653">藏師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0894c26"/>落髮。<date key="j20154742016757" notAfter-iso="+0809-08-04" notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29"><name>元和</name>初</date>受具於杭之<placeName key="PLG00000000023">天竺寺</placeName>。凡百經律<lb
ed="T" n="0894c27"/>論疏鈔，嗜其腴潤。一旦芒屩策杖，詣<placeName key="PL000000018628">洪州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0894c28"/>禪門，洞達心要，虛往實歸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1372"/>。却於本郡大慶<lb
ed="T" n="0894c29"/>寺<!--找不到此地-->，求益者提訓，凡二十餘載，為<placeName key="PL000000000197">江左</placeName>名僧。<pb ed="T" n="0895a" xml:id="T50.2061.0895a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0895a01"/>見儒士能青眼<ptr target="#n2086"/>，故名輩多與之遊，往往戲<lb
ed="T" n="0895a02"/>為詩句，辭皆錯愕。凡從事廉問護戎於<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0895a03"/>入境籍聲實而造其戶，不獨能誘，亦善與<lb
ed="T" n="0895a04"/>人交者。<date key="j20231922026427" notAfter-iso="+0836-01-25" notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18"><name>大和</name>中</date>遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，路出<placeName key="PL000000042189">京邑</placeName>，一夕而<lb
ed="T" n="0895a05"/>去。前護戎<persName key="A013923">郄志榮</persName>、<persName key="A013924">宋常春</persName>二內侍尤味其道，<lb
ed="T" n="0895a06"/>孜孜遠招。<date key="j20264282026797" notAfter-iso="+0837-01-29" notBefore-iso="+0836-01-26"><name>開成</name>初</date>再至<placeName key="PL000000042189">京國</placeName>，二貴人同力唱<lb
ed="T" n="0895a07"/>和，牽裓虐留，致<placeName key="PL000000042180">安國寺</placeName>大方丈以居之。<placeName key="PL000000042189">王<lb
ed="T" n="0895a08"/>畿</placeName>龍象，莫不欽重。無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>召入為供奉大德，<lb
ed="T" n="0895a09"/>非所好也，徇俗受之。然歸歟之<anchor xml:id="beg0895sgsz1"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0895sgsz1"/>，未甞少<lb
ed="T" n="0895a10"/>棄。<date key="j20245332024533" when-iso="+0830-11-18">四年十月二十五日</date>囑累弟子訖，奄然而<lb
ed="T" n="0895a11"/>寂，春秋五十六，夏三十二。<persName key="A013923">郄</persName>、<persName key="A013924">宋</persName>二家率財權<lb
ed="T" n="0895a12"/>瘞于<g ref="#CB05908">[滻-文+(立-一)]</g>水，東人皆悲之，門人<persName key="A010653">鑑諸</persName>後歸葬<lb
ed="T" n="0895a13"/>于<placeName key="PL000000023253">崇山</placeName>之南，華嚴寺<!--找不到此地-->起塔。<date key="j20293522029735" notAfter-iso="+0845-02-14" notBefore-iso="+0844-01-28">會<anchor xml:id="beg0895sgsz3"/>昌<anchor xml:id="end0895sgsz3"/>四年</date>，起居舍<lb
ed="T" n="0895a14"/>人<persName key="A013926">韋絢</persName>為碑紀代焉。</p>
